{"tid":792014,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(黑夜之神) 公路出現蝙蝠車！警車閃燈截停 結局超展開","createTime":"2018-08-24T08:55:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-27T02:45:05.000Z","uid":184679,"like":269,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"eaeb993931b3863b82f7324eb8ccb81868e972a4","tid":792014,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T08:55:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2018-08-24/656/20180824003119.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2018-08-24%2F656%2F20180824003119.jpg&h=0b888b1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">車道出現蝙蝠車！警車閃燈示意攔檢 (圖翻攝自youtube/New York Post)</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n電影裡的正義角色，總是讓不少人想模仿，若在路上看見蝙蝠俠，肯定讓人搶著合照。加拿大安大略省馬路上，日前出現一輛蝙蝠車，由於外型相當吸睛，讓人忍不住多看好幾眼，豈料他最後也被警察盯上，警車閃燈示意他停靠接受臨檢，沒想到警員一下車，居然是想與蝙蝠俠合照。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PXzVWaNkitg#action=share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DPXzVWaNkitg%23action%3Dshare&d=itMRmcMEBhBK6NMbRZTM%2BP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=17da9393\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PXzVWaNkitg#action=share</a><br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，一名網友日前在安大略省馬路上，看見一輛神複製電影的蝙蝠車，隨後警車隨後便閃燈，要求駕駛靠邊停車，一名身穿蝙蝠裝的男子便走下車，接受員警的巡查，起初拍攝者以為是蝙蝠俠超速，或不合法改車，豈料兩人沒講幾句話，蝙蝠俠便開車離開，讓拍攝者直呼「太好了吧！」，並將影片上傳網路。<br />\n<br />\n而這名蝙蝠俠Coser其實是史蒂芬(Stephen Lawrence)，在當地小有名氣，平時是一名口可樂員工，因為非常喜歡蝙蝠俠，才會將自己與愛車，還原蝙蝠俠電影裡的模樣，有時還會參加慈善活動或至醫院，帶給需要幫助的孩子們快樂，而他也強調，這輛蝙蝠車是合法改裝上路，因此沒有問題。<br />\n<br />\n事後史帝芬也表示，18日回家途中，由於他的車外型太引人注目，導致許多人跟在他後面拍照，他認為這樣會造成交通問題，甚至非常危險，於是發現警車後便上前求助，只是護送到一半時，警車突然閃燈示意停靠，原本他還不清楚發生什麼事情，直到下車才知道，原來是員警覺得機會難得，因此想跟蝙蝠俠合照，而當地警局也證實此事，更表示此舉並沒不好，還可拉近警民關係。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hottopic.chinatimes.com/20180824003096-260809\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhottopic.chinatimes.com%2F20180824003096-260809&d=itMRmcMEBhBK6NMbRZTM%2BP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=86f94e77\" target=\"_blank\">http://hottopic.chinatimes.com/20180824003096-260809</a>"},{"pid":"0b6a163183bcf87142205da9f34899419041d793","tid":792014,"uid":101110,"like":616,"dislike":3,"score":613,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T09:01:53.000Z","msg":"平時是一名口可樂員工，因為非常喜歡蝙蝠俠，才會將自己與愛車，還原蝙蝠俠電影裡的模樣，有時還會參加慈善活動或至醫院，帶給需要幫助的孩子們快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實生活好應該係噉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f39cc5acb80b6664a5411f907b801215aa94df78","tid":792014,"uid":36296,"like":122,"dislike":2,"score":120,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T09:02:28.000Z","msg":"香港有邊條路可以比呢架車行 而又唔會hi到地下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77713117557061db65e3e4c1dc68ce69077e1a13","tid":792014,"uid":132137,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T09:03:19.000Z","msg":"型撚到"},{"pid":"00637c758cc274c381f82d6ed41586abf11a953f","tid":792014,"uid":44562,"like":69,"dislike":0,"score":69,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T09:04:38.000Z","msg":"咩叫超展開 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9299e2741debcfe834e3548aa7cfa7d079e877ef","tid":792014,"uid":184679,"like":297,"dislike":2,"score":295,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T09:09:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.magicalquote.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/Bruce-Wayne-the-dark-knight-rises.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.magicalquote.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2014%2F07%2FBruce-Wayne-the-dark-knight-rises.jpg&h=0415bfd3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f1cb7faaba9a7cbc0b6a3a8f8fea32357845bbfa","tid":792014,"uid":40932,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"00637c758cc274c381f82d6ed41586abf11a953f","tid":792014,"uid":44562,"like":69,"dislike":0,"score":69,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T09:04:38.000Z","msg":"咩叫超展開 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"repl